name: Beyond Good and Evil_Friedrich Wilhelm Nietzsche

oMeta.description: Since the French Revolution the influence of woman in Europe has DECLINED in proportion as she has increased her rights and claims; and the "emancipation of woman," insofar as it is desired and demanded by women themselves (and not only by masculine shallow-pates), thus proves to be a remarkable symptom of the increased weakening and deadening of the most womanly instincts.
oMeta.title: Beyond Good And Evil
